    Class Description
    BaseModelURIProcessingStepParameter
    Parameter for specifying the base URI to use for the knowledge base model, entities, relations and, in general, every piece of data in a model that should be identified by a URI.

    Parameter for specifying whether the resulting Apache Jena dataset should be compacted after all write operations on it are done.
